==English==
===Noun===
'''hydrocortisone'''
#{{biochemistry}} a [[steroid]] [[hormone]], produced by the [[adrenal cortex]], that [[regulate]]s the [[metabolism]] of [[carbohydrate]]s and maintains [[blood pressure]]
#{{medicine}} a [[synthetic]] version of this hormone used to treat [[Addison's disease]] and other conditions
